# Test ve kalite

## PR öncesi (ilgiliyse zorunlu)

- `pnpm typecheck`, `pnpm lint`, `pnpm test`
- Integration / E2E-smoke (`pnpm smoke:routes`, `pnpm smoke:navigation`, `pnpm smoke:e2e`)
- Tenant isolation, permission guard, approval policy, webhook signature/idempotency, AI proposal snapshot, audit/timeline write

## Tamamlanmış sayılmaz

- Kritik guard/approval/webhook/AI action/tenant değişikliği **testsiz**.
- `apps/web/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo` commit’e alınmaz.

## UI işi

`pnpm --filter @hallederiz/web typecheck`, `pnpm --filter @hallederiz/ui typecheck`, `pnpm smoke:navigation`.

## Referans

- `docs/development/QUALITY_GATES.md`, `.github/workflows/quality-gate.yml`
